<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>버티(Vertee) 개인정보처리방침</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.7;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111;
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #a3e635;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #222;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #a3e635;
        }
